@orders_api_HostAddress = https://orders-api-dev-eus-10.azurewebsites.net
### Get all orders
GET {{orders_api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Get order by id
GET {{orders_api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1002
Accept: application/json

### Create a new order
POST {{orders_api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "orderId": 2001,
  "customerName": "Customer 004",
  "amount": 79.00
}